# React component checklist

Reference implementations: `item`, `attachment`, `empty`.

## File structure

```
packages/react/src/components/{name}/{name}.tsx
apps/docs/src/app/(app)/docs/components/{name}/
  page.mdx
  example/default.tsx
  example/index.ts
```

## Component code

- Import `cn`, `cva`, `VariantProps` from `@nerdfish/utils/class`
- Use `@base-ui/react` (`useRender`, `mergeProps`) for polymorphic parts — see `breadcrumb`, `button`
- Relative imports for sibling components (`../button/button`), never `@/`
- Export a named `*Props` type per subcomponent (`ComponentProps<'div'>`, `useRender.ComponentProps<'button'>`, etc.)
- Use `function` declarations, not arrow exports
- Add `data-slot="{name}-{part}"` on every part; root gets `group/{name}` for child targeting
- Variants via `cva` with `defaultVariants`; compose with `cn(variants({ ... }), className)`
- Only add `'use client'` when the file needs client APIs (most primitives omit it)

## package.json export

Add alphabetically to `packages/react/package.json` exports:

```json
"./{name}": "./src/components/{name}/{name}.tsx"
```

Run `pnpm build` in `packages/react` so docs resolve `@nerdfish/react/{name}`.

## Docs

1. `page.mdx` — `DocsPageHeader` + `ComponentExample` sections
2. `example/*.tsx` — `'use client'`, import from `@nerdfish/react/{name}`
3. `example/index.ts` — re-export examples
4. `apps/docs/src/app/(app)/docs/components/component-examples.tsx` — add export
5. `apps/docs/src/nav.ts` — add link (set `status: 'new'` for new components)

## Styling

Follow `design-tokens.mdc`. Use semantic `@nerdfish/react` tokens — never raw Tailwind spacing (`gap-2`, `px-2.5`) or generic color aliases (`bg-card`, `text-muted-foreground`).

## CSS utilities

New animation utilities → `packages/react/src/styles/animations.css`
Layout/misc utilities → `packages/react/src/styles/utilities.css`
Import new partials from `global.css`; don't inline large blocks in `global.css`.
